{"tid":2133301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大校委會主席李國章: 戴耀廷是罪犯，港大不容罪犯為職員","createTime":"2020-07-31T03:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T14:59:50.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9cdb9135f818340099f71dd8c0375b0bcd02b41d","tid":2133301,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:56:00.000Z","msg":"港大校委會主席李國章周四 (30/7) 接受《南華早報》專訪表示，拒絕外間指解僱戴耀廷是政治決定的說法，並指戴是罪犯，港大不容罪犯為職員<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷與港大校友會都認為，校委會應該等到法院上訴程序完成後才作出決定，否則可能是「違反程序正義」；戴的上訴訂於明年三月開始。然而，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">李指如果戴上訴再失敗，要排期到終審法院審理，需時 1&ndash;2 年時間。校委會已與法律顧問討論，最終認為情況很簡單：戴今天是罪犯。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n李國章指，如果戴上訴成功，將會重新審視決定。他表示，過去港大也有職員因被判有罪而被解僱，所以戴並非唯一一個受影響的職員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E5%8D%97%E6%97%A9%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F-%E6%9D%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%AB%A0-%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7%E6%98%AF%E7%BD%AA%E7%8A%AF-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E7%BD%AA%E7%8A%AF%E5%81%9A%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%2595%258F-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25AB%25A0-%25E6%2588%25B4%25E8%2580%2580%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%258A%25AF-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%258A%25AF%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG118MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=23c98642\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%2595%258F-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25AB%25A0-%25E6%2588%25B4%25E8%2580%2580%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%258A%25AF-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%258A%25AF%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2